{
  "Specifically controls the volume of tornadoes during gameplay": "Громкость торнадо в игре.",
  "When enabled, aligns the original and the reverse audio stream to negate the output inside the input, resulting in effective echo cancellation.": "Убирает эхо, вычитая исходящий звук из входящего сигнала микрофона.",
  "Controls the game's display resolution. Higher values produce sharper visuals but may impact performance.": "Разрешение экрана. Выше — чётче, но тяжелее для ПК.",
  "Controls Lumen Global Illumination. When enabled, ray-traced lighting allows light to bounce between surfaces for more realistic results. Has a significant performance impact.": "Глобальное освещение Lumen. Реалистичнее, но сильно нагружает ПК.",
  "Controls the quality level of the selected anti-aliasing method. Higher values improve image clarity at a performance cost.": "Качество выбранного сглаживания. Выше — чётче, но ниже FPS.",
  "Controls the resolution the game is rendered at before being scaled to your screen. Higher values produce a sharper image but reduce performance. Lower values improve performance but may look softer or blurrier.": "Внутреннее разрешение до масштабирования. Выше — чётче, ниже — выше FPS.",
  "Controls the quality and resolution of shadows. Higher values produce sharper, more accurate shadows.": "Качество и разрешение теней.",
  "Controls the quality of reflections on surfaces like water and shiny materials. Higher values improve reflection detail and accuracy.": "Качество отражений на воде и блестящих поверхностях.",
  "Controls the resolution of textures used in the game. Higher values improve surface detail but require more video memory.": "Разрешение текстур. Выше — детальнее, больше видеопамяти.",
  "Controls the quality of visual effects including particles, translucency, refraction, and screen-space reflections. Higher values increase the quality and accuracy of these effects.": "Качество частиц, прозрачности и экранных отражений.",
  "Controls the quality of volumetric fog. Higher values improve fog detail and smoothness but may reduce performance.": "Качество объёмного тумана.",
  "Controls the quality of bloom (glow around bright lights). Higher values produce smoother, more natural bloom but may reduce performance.": "Качество bloom (свечение ярких источников).",
  "Adjusts the strength of the CRT post-processing effect.": "Сила эффекта ЭЛТ на экране.",
  "Controls the strength of camera shake when taking damage. Lower values reduce or disable shake.": "Сила тряски камеры при получении урона.",
  "Controls the strength of camera shake when interacting with items or objects. Lower values reduce or disable shake.": "Сила тряски камеры при взаимодействии с предметами.",
  "This is a new tire, you can replace any broken tire on the van with this one. First you need a scissors jack to lift up the van and a toolbox to remove the old tire. Once you do that, just press [{Key0}] to install the new one.": "Новое колесо: домкрат + инструмент снять старое, затем [{Key0}] поставить.",
  "A collectable! Take it back to the collectables box on the van and you will get a bonus for your trouble (only if you survive, otherwise it will NOT go to your next of kin).": "Находка! Несите в ящик фургона — бонус, если выживете.",
  "Acid rain will damage you constantly while you are not under a roof. Should you get an umbrella, please be a team player and share it with other employees.": "Кислота ранит без крыши. Зонт лучше делить с командой.",
  "Pay attention employee, certain dangerous actions will require you to be very precise. You must press [{Key0}] when the indicator is on the green area to successfully perform the action. If you fail, you might take damage. Some interactions will require multiple presses to be completed.": "Опасно: жмите [{Key0}] в зелёной зоне. Промах — урон. Иногда нужно несколько нажатий.",
