  "Collect 100 information related collectables.": "Собери 100 информационных находок.",
  "Collect 50 items found in the city.": "Собери 50 находок в городе.",
  "Collect 100 items found in the city.": "Собери 100 находок в городе.",
  "Collect 500 items found in the city.": "Собери 500 находок в городе.",
  "Throw a dart into a big tornado, close enough so it doesn’t fall to the ground. “It’s the suck zone”": "Брось дротик в большой торнадо так, чтобы он не упал. «Это зона всасывания»",
  "1. Disconnect the battery cables;\r\n2. Disconnect the battery using the toolbox;\r\n3. Find a new, working battery;\r\n4. Install the new battery;\r\n5. Connect the cables again using the toolbox.": "1. Отсоедините кабели;\r\n2. Снимите АКБ инструментом;\r\n3. Найдите рабочий АКБ;\r\n4. Установите новый;\r\n5. Подключите кабели инструментом.",
  "The monitors let you see what other employees are doing, and help you work better as a team (if you see anyone slacking off please report it).": "Monitory: chto delayut drugie. Lentyaev — v raport.",
  "Communication is key. To use the walkie-talkie press [{Key0}] to turn it on and off and [{Key1}] to talk to your teammates. Please limit conversation to work-related topics, such as your survival.": "Raciya: [{Key0}] vkl/vykl, [{Key1}] govorit. Tolko po delu.",
  "This is the storage box. You have to bring all collectables you find here, newspapers, VHS tapes, files, and the like, otherwise you will not get any rewards out of them, company policy.": "Sklad: nesite syuda gazety, VHS, fayly — inache net nagrad.",
  "Crowbars can help you open barricaded doors. Don’t worry about breaking and entering charges, these houses are going to be broken soon anyway. To use it, go towards any barricaded door and press [{Key0}].": "Lom: k zabitoj dveri i [{Key0}].",
  "Flashlights can help you illuminate dark places. Press [{Key0}] to turn them on and off. Don’t leave them on unnecessarily, their batteries run out!.": "Fonari: [{Key0}] vkl/vykl. Ne zhgi batareyku zrya.",
  "Portable conductors will protect you from lightning. No need to do anything special, just hold them out and you’ll be fine (probably).": "Provodnik ot molniy — prosto derzhite.",
  "Push to Talk": "Govori (PTT)",
  "Color Vision Filter": "Filtr zreniya cveta",
  "Color Vision Filter Intensity": "Sila filtra zreniya cveta",
  "Mouse Smoothing": "Sglazh. myshi",
  "Private": "Lichnyy",
  "Applies a color filter designed to improve color distinction for different types of color vision deficiency.": "Filtr dlya luchshego razlicheniya cvetov pri narushenii cvetovospriyatiya.",
  "Smooths mouse movement for the camera and cursor. When enabled, movement feels less immediate but more fluid. When disabled, mouse input responds more directly.": "Sglazhivayet mysh dlya kamery i kursora. Vklyucheno — plavnee, vyklyucheno — rezkoy.",
  "Controls whose drawings you can see on the whiteboard.": "Chyi risunki vidny na doske.",
  "Running can help you get to places quickly or escape danger, just be careful to not “run” out of stamina or you’ll have to stop and rest (break time will be automatically deducted from your paycheck).": "Beg bystree, no stamina konchaetsya — otdyh s zarplaty.",
  "Running can help you get to places quickly or escape danger, just be careful to not \"run\" out of stamina or you'll have to stop and rest (break time will be automatically deducted from your paycheck).": "Beg uskorayet, no stamina konchayetsya - otdyh spishet s zarplaty.",
  "Defibrillators can bring a fellow employee back from the brink of death!, it can also let them keep working for us. To use it, hold [{Key0}] to charge it up, and aim at a downed employee to revive them.": "Defib: derzhite [{Key0}], celtes v lezhashchego.",
  "You are looking at the van’s engine, your only hope for escape. It’s also APEX’s property, so treat it with care. Interact with any highlighted element to get more information on how to fix it. Don’t forget to check the fuel tank and the tires later.": "Dvigatel — shans na pobeg. Tyknite podsvetku kak chinit.",
  "You are looking at the van's engine, your only hope for escape. It's also APEX's property, so treat it with care. Interact with any highlighted element to get more information on how to fix it. Don't forget to check the fuel tank and the tires later.": "Dvigatel van - shans na pobeg. Tyknite podsvetku: kak chinit. Potom bak i shiny.",
  "Crowbars can help you open barricaded doors. Don't worry about breaking and entering charges, these houses are going to be broken soon anyway. To use it, go towards any barricaded door and press [{Key0}].": "Lom: k zabitoj dveri i [{Key0}].",
  "Flashlights can help you illuminate dark places. Press [{Key0}] to turn them on and off. Don't leave them on unnecessarily, their batteries run out!.": "Fonari: [{Key0}] vkl/vykl. Ne zhgi batareyku zrya.",
  "Portable conductors will protect you from lightning. No need to do anything special, just hold them out and you'll be fine (probably).": "Provodnik ot molniy — prosto derzhite.",
